## Interface: 11508
## Title: Talent Planner
## Version: 4.3.0
## Author: Moregelen, Sveng
## Notes: Shows what order you should spend talent points in. Import from Wowhead, Talent Planner web UI, or JSON. Compatible with WoW Classic Anniversary Edition.
## SavedVariables: TalentPlannerAccountSavedSequences, TalentPlannerAccountCollapsedClasses, TalentPlannerAccountNextSequenceId
## SavedVariablesPerCharacter: IsTalentPlannerExpanded, TalentPlannerTalents, TalentPlannerSavedSequences, TalentPlannerActiveClass, TalentPlannerActiveSequenceIds
